Use ament target dependencies

The previous use of ${..._LIBRARIES} and ${..._TARGETS} caused
absolute paths in INTERFACE_LINK_LIBRARIES, triggering
do_package_qa failures (buildpaths).

This change:
   - switches ROS dependencies to ament_target_dependencies()
   - links non-ROS libraries (TinyXML2, fmt) via CMake targets
   - removes use of ${pal_statistics_INCLUDE_DIRS}
   - adds missing dependency on pal_statistics_msgs

Upstream-Status: Pending
Assisted-by: M365 Copilot:GPT-5-chat
Signed-off by: Rob Woolley <rob.woolley@windriver.com>

Index: hardware-interface-6.3.2-1/CMakeLists.txt
===================================================================
